Description: MultiFlexi VaultWarden credential prototype
 VaultWarden/Bitwarden secrets credential prototype for MultiFlexi core.
 Provides the CredentialProtoType class that defines VaultWarden URL,
 user login, password and folder configuration fields.

Package: multiflexi-vaultwarden-ui
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, multiflexi-vaultwarden (= ${binary:Version}), multiflexi-web
Description: MultiFlexi VaultWarden UI components
 VaultWarden connection dialog for MultiFlexi web interface.
 Tests server connectivity, authentication and folder access,
